<h3 id="change-mode">CHange MODe</h3>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">chmod [options] mode[, mode] file1 [file2 ...]</code></p>

<h5 id="eg">e.g.</h5>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">chmod o-r file.type</code> : other ì‚¬ìš©ìì˜ Read ê¶Œí•œ ì‚­ì œ</p>

